item.title: Port forwarding help
item.dc:creator: @kiamyhelp kiamyhelp
item.description:
@kiamyhelp wrote:

Remove your udp one. leave the other one.

If that doesnt work delete both.

Protocol is TCP

If you can leave the timeout blank. (if you cant im sorry i use linksys)

port: 43594-43594

Host Port: 43594

App Type is FTP ( Im pretty sure) But if im wrong it shouldnt matter.

Make Sure you open up port 43594 in your firewall “exceptions”
